{"tid":2023226,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅致光：若直接將補貼發給僱員未必可保就業","createTime":"2020-05-19T00:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T02:28:45.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"eea74d3c467155db6b1435632c24da693cba2b22","tid":2023226,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T00:54:54.000Z","msg":"勞工及福利局長羅致光，在一個電台節目表示，政府推出「保就業計劃」，是希望僱主不要裁員甚至結業，否則疫情好轉時，企業難以盡快重新起步。他又指，若果政府直接將資助發放給僱員，未必可以保就業，僱主都仍然有可能會裁員。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光又指，計算補貼額的方程式，是考慮到企業近月人手可能有自然流失，一些企業即使將獲得的補貼，全數用來出糧，都未必可以捱下去，所以當局保守以3月份受聘人數計算，而僱主申領補貼的月份，受薪僱員人數不得少於3月，否則僱主須交罰款。"},{"pid":"eda654be94e9e43a6f0dc33b6635220a2e7f4014","tid":2023226,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T00:55:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288418\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1288418&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F4D442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=d3b9cefd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288418</a>"},{"pid":"f20fb1c9575d0b48f1d73866e32ef2bc0a5f270e","tid":2023226,"uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T01:24:26.000Z","msg":"即係只想做靚個經濟數據，理得你死"},{"pid":"8adfd0371afd46aebc9cef5b9a2829c70d180e67","tid":2023226,"uid":194298,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T01:27:44.000Z","msg":"依仔友真係CLS"},{"pid":"6f5acdb8460cbcd45327cdcd4472e5ce5169f522","tid":2023226,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T01:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/